title: AYG Comedy Podcast: Shuli Egar - Las Vegas Kid
description:
AYG comedy podcast presents stand up comedian, podcast host, & Howard Stern personality Shuli Egar. Shuli talks living in Las Vegas and working at the casinos. You know Shuli Egar from Your Mom's House Podcast (YMH), Howard Stern Show & more!

Comedians H. Foley and Kevin Ryan are self proclaimed GARBAGE. Each week a new stand up comedian gets put to the test. Steal shampoo from hotels? Own a George Foreman Grill? Ever worn JNCO Jeans?
